<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子的话深深地伤害了小美人鱼的心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼的心碎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31163</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她不能说话，没法告诉王子是自己在暴风雨中救了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37409</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼无法告诉王子，如果王子和梅丹结婚，她就会死。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37410</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有声音的小美人鱼连一句话也说不出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我到底做了什么？” 她想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真不该把声音给海巫婆。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼就算伤心，也哭不出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为人鱼不会哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她只能伤心地看着王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子不明白小美人鱼为什么伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没想到我能再见到梅丹。” 他开心地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我亲爱的小伙伴，替我高兴吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，王国卫兵们骑着马宣布婚礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，王室成员们行进穿过城里，一直走到中心广场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在那里，王子和梅丹公主手拉手结了婚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们接吻时，人群欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有小美人鱼心都碎了，在婚礼上一直抱着新娘的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她回想起自己以前在海底王国的生活和奶奶的抚摸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我抛弃了我的家和家人们。” 小美人鱼想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我失去了我美丽的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，我失去了我的王子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当太阳在海上升起时，我会死的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，婚宴在大船上举行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子和他的新娘，还有所有的客人都来到甲板上开大派对。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>夜晚安静、晴朗，就像小美人鱼第一次见到王子那天一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>五颜六色的灯照亮了甲板。满天放着烟花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船员和客人们一起随着音乐跳舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王子走向小美人鱼，鞠躬问：“我的小伙伴，你能为我的客人跳舞吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我能跟你跳舞，我的王子。” 她想说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼一个人跳舞跳到了中间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像平时一样，她双脚疼得要命。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但这次，她不觉得疼，因为她的心碎了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198831</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她知道这会是她在地上的最后一晚，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她再也见不到她的王子了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼得不到灵魂，她会变成波浪上的泡沫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跳着舞，像中了魔法，没有思想，没有梦想，也没有希望。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小美人鱼的舞蹈很迷人，让客人们着了迷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的脚好像中了魔法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，音乐停止了，小美人鱼也停了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她寻找王子，但他已经走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那幸福的夫妇已经去睡了。” 一位客人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好像在回答小美人鱼心中的疑问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们祝他们幸福吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>甲板上，有一个金色的帐篷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>篷里，王室夫妇坐在床上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>客人们欢呼着，王子亲了新娘，手指穿过新娘的头发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>